I use one maybe two discs ever.  Normally I save my disc for defensive becuause I am generally the MA or SA.  If I think it is going to be a fast Trak style fight I'll use fellstrike, or if the mob is 1 or 2 pct health &amp; the MA is doing fine.  The one time I tried using aggressive I got my ass handed to me because I generated too much agro.<br>
