<br>
Positioning:  We wall just about everything.  In order to keep the MA from having to continually flip the mob, we position a fair number of plate class melees in front of the mob.  That means eating a few ripostes.  If a warrior is aggressive &amp; eats what would normally be a 900 dmg riposte its going to be more like 1300.  That means not only are you a mana sponge, you will die if you are already low on health.<br>
